for outline see: http://meetingorganizer.copernicus.org/EGU2012/EGU2012-680.pdf

tested on Debian sid with:
- gcc-snapshot (for C++11 compliant g++)
- gfortran (default version to be compatible with packaged .mod files)

$ export FC="gfortran -I/usr/include/"
$ export CXX=/usr/lib/gcc-snapshot/bin/g++
$ cmake . -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release 
$ make
